4611,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"想飲喜茶 係咁㗎啦"},{"pid":"564a47f889fb305f4e9cab0a80e4d53418e8dd0b","tid":1044611,"uid":28355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔又推舊ぽ打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98cd0b1fed09a3711d9df7fa076a4aa1b93ab46","tid":1044611,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"100年前未有cctv係咪無人非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c9d733412b6b8be9764c6f5727c5fb385a4576","tid":1044611,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"564a47f889fb305f4e9cab0a80e4d53418e8dd0b","tid":1044611,"uid":28355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔又推舊ぽ打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"上面個Facebook係回帶之前定之後呢"},{"pid":"85963049a32174ae870817a2bc5fdff2df4c65d3","tid":1044611,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdccc7bdb68b0125730257fc6c9b536002c256fa","tid":1044611,"uid":57844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06c1bec77b512032246612fd53ff034d0f88515e","tid":1044611,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"971fe72fba769dd0a991be161f34c0a414bd7171","tid":1044611,"uid":57844,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"應該搵2019 新聞去證明無進步過<br />\n回帶只係打飛機行為"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"你係咪無睇新聞<br />\n咩大抓捕<br />\n大陸根本無法治保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"我有睇新聞，我講你個POST<br />\n明就明，唔明就黎明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"內地無非禮罪難討公道<br />\n不過即使女事主向內地公安報警，也未必可討回公道。廣東宏安信律師事務所律師童建華指，內地並沒有「非禮罪」，較接近的控罪只有「強制猥褻、侮辱婦女罪」。非禮行為若沒有令對方受傷，一般只會進行「批評教育」，「如達唔到輕傷以上，或者有一定性接觸，嗰啲刑法上處理唔到；舉例地鐵上有人偷拍，唔係好嚴重就了結咗件事」。除非有畫面被拍下、證據確鑿及引起公眾不安，才可能被拘留及罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8d8b5c2ea39385246f35863b69d40c902c190f","tid":1044611,"uid":181680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"痴漢鐵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ad3c54899e963d3a57f865d649525d956f64c2","tid":1044611,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"符合國情，港女北上應融合中國文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}